data.description: This 3 bedroom brick ranch home was completely renovated in 2018 with new windows, HVAC, electrical, plumbing, sheetrock, flooring, cabinetry, countertops, appliances and water heater per the previous owner. The interior features an open concept with a spacious pantry and laundry room plus an attached garage and fenced back yard. Contact Ginger at 270 871-1514 for more details or to schedule a showing.
